{"service_name": "Methods Advisory: Sourcing and Procurement Services", "service_id": "4983754003054592", "company_name": "Methods Advisory Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Methods Advisory Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Methods Advisory: Sourcing and Procurement Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Methods Advisory delivers end-to-end procurement support, from a turnkey solution, including full procurement management, to providing selected specialist support to enhance your team along the procurement timeline.  We are fully conversant with all types of procurement process and EU Directives and we are particularly experienced in conducting Competitive Dialogue.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Market Assessment/ analysis and testing,  pre-procurement, soft and hard\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Sourcing and procurement strategies;  designed to ensure best value\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Evaluation/ selection methodologies; robust and value for money\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business investment cases; experienced in 5 case models\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Financial and economic modelling and analysis to support procurement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supplier negotiation; experienced at leading competitive dialogue\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Procurement management; end to end turnkey or specialist input\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Commercial deal execution/ contract award to meet legal requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Procurement and commercial advice including commercial legal\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     UK Central Government/ Assemblies, Healthcare, Local Government/ Authorities\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Identification of optimal procurement route to go to market\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Designed to deliver outcomes against legal and regulatory requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Robust evaluation/ selection methodologies to ensure value for money\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides assurance that business case will withstand scrutiny\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support can flex with client needs and funding\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Competitive dialogue resulting in compliant competitive bids against outcomes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure reduced risk of challenge and successful award\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stronger deals with better value and more robust contracts\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Able to provide fixed price or savings-based commercial arrangements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     No procurement we have supported has ever been successfully challenged\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3300 to \u00a31750 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92308/4983754003054592-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"http